description:
Did you know that our loved ALFONS TREKNER has a bad brother? 

-YES- he has!

His name is RENKERT SNOFLA.

ALFONS is positive; RENKERT is negative.
ALFONS looks to the right. RENKERT looks to the left.

This is Renkert Snofla. He hates the sun and he hates Fish. He is not afraid of Dogs. But he hates swimming. He can fly since his second birthday. Renkert SnoflaÂ´s  favorite meal are suassages. And Steak. He loves his name. But he hates travelling.
name: RENKERT SNOFLA - The one and only
